
This directory contains an article written by Greg Walters describing
how to build an application with two GUI's which communicate with each
other. This article appeared first in Full Circle magazine issue
155. Full Circle is a free, independent, monthly PDF magazine
dedicated to the Ubuntu family of Linux operating systems. Each month,
it contains helpful how-to articles and reader submitted stories. The
home page is https://fullcirclemagazine.org/. It contains many articles
on many subjects about using Python written by Greg Walters.